sentence.text: Mining GWAS databases revealed association of cis-eSNPs for more than 50 genes with T2D (e.g. endocytosis, RBMS1, biological_process), gluco-metabolic phenotypes (e.g. INPP5E, SNX17, antigen processing and presentation of peptide antigen via MHC class I, FN3KRP), and obesity (e.g. POMC, CPEB4).
